3 action packed movies in lovely Blu Ray High Def all for a reasonable price. Includes  "Independence Day", "The Day After Tomorrow" and "I Robot". All movies are action packed and have a good cast. When packaged together = a winning combination.
I love all these movies

Entire top half of case was cracked and falling off.  I don't know if it was because of the shipping or if the case was so old it started to crack.  Either way, I didn't want to wait to return it and get another one since all 3 movies are in excellent condition.
Great value for the money.  I love two of the movies and like the other one very much.  So getting all three for this price is a great value.
Awesome movie package.

There are 2 versions of Independence Day.  A long and a short.  On my original desk, a DVD, both versions were included, the version on this disc does not give you that option.  I robot would not play the last half of the movie.  I cleaned it twice with a. DVD cleaning kit without solving the problem.  Jumper played all the way with no hiccups on the same Blu-ray player.  I actually found a thumbprint on the I robot desk.

I had no problem getting this disc set replaced by Amazon.  Still, I'm going to get the short version of Independence Day.
